---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "About Oxyzen London - Your Trusted Oxygen Therapy Provider";
const description = "Learn about Oxyzen London, the leading oxygen therapy clinic in London. Discover our history, mission, and commitment to providing high-quality hyperbaric oxygen treatments.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Oxyzen London</h1>
    
    <section id="our-story" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Oxyzen London was established in 2010 with a vision to bring cutting-edge hyperbaric oxygen therapy to the heart of London. As pioneers in the field, we have consistently strived to provide the highest quality oxygen treatments, combining advanced technology with expert care.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Our journey began when our founder, Dr. Elizabeth Chambers, recognised the immense potential of hyperbaric oxygen therapy in enhancing health and wellness. Inspired by her research and personal experiences, she set out to create a sanctuary where individuals could access this revolutionary treatment in a comfortable and professional environment.</p>
      <p>Over the years, we have grown from a small clinic to become London's premier destination for oxygen therapy. Our commitment to excellence and continuous improvement has earned us the trust of thousands of clients, including professional athletes, celebrities, and health-conscious individuals from all walks of life.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="mission-values" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission and Values</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">At Oxyzen London, our mission is to enhance the health and wellbeing of our clients through the power of hyperbaric oxygen therapy. We are dedicated to providing personalised, evidence-based treatments that deliver tangible results.</p>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Our Core Values:</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Excellence:</strong> We strive for the highest standards in everything we do, from our state-of-the-art equipment to our customer service.</li>
        <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We continuously explore new advancements in oxygen therapy to offer our clients the most effective treatments available.</li>
        <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> We operate with complete transparency and honesty, always putting our clients' best interests first.</li>
        <li><strong>Empathy:</strong> We understand that each client's journey is unique, and we provide compassionate care tailored to individual needs.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="team" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Expert Team</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">At Oxyzen London, we pride ourselves on our team of highly qualified professionals who are passionate about hyperbaric oxygen therapy and its potential to transform lives. Our staff includes:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Board-certified hyperbaric physicians</li>
        <li>Experienced hyperbaric technicians</li>
        <li>Certified nursing staff</li>
        <li>Wellness coaches and nutritionists</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-4">Each member of our team undergoes rigorous training and stays up-to-date with the latest developments in hyperbaric medicine to ensure that our clients receive the best possible care.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="facilities">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">State-of-the-Art Facilities</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Our clinic is equipped with the latest hyperbaric oxygen chambers, designed to provide a safe, comfortable, and effective treatment experience. Our facilities include:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Multiple hyperbaric chambers to accommodate various treatment needs</li>
        <li>Spacious, private treatment rooms</li>
        <li>Advanced monitoring systems for patient safety</li>
        <li>Comfortable waiting areas for companions</li>
        <li>On-site consultation rooms for personalised treatment planning</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-4">We maintain the highest standards of cleanliness and safety, ensuring that our clients can focus on their treatment and recovery in a peaceful, stress-free environment.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
